      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Giant Hunter's Handbook pg. 33</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 5th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +2,000 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbolN.gif\" title=\"See the Organized Play FAQ for clarifications about the fitting armor special ability\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>A <em>fitting</em> shield or suit of armor instantly shrinks or grows to suit the size of any creature that picks it up unless it is currently worn by another creature. It reverts to its original size 1 round after it leaves that creature's possession.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>resize item</em>; <strong>Price</strong> 1,000 gp</p>",
